      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she\u2019s a total beauty! This car is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept, spotless, and up-to-date on every single service. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
