    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.1), a pinnacle of analog driver engagement. This example features the M97.01 3.8L flat-six power plant, delivering 355 hp through a precise G97 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is optimized with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior lateral grip and neutral cornering dynamics. Mechanically flawless, the engine has undergone a documented borescope inspection with zero evidence of cylinder bore scoring and features an updated IMS solution. The braking system utilizes four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing exceptional thermal management and pedal modulation. Finished in a paint-corrected exterior with zero rock chips or swirling, this 997 retains its factory structural rigidity and aerodynamic balance. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
